SUMMARY:Public Star Party
LOCATION:Robert Ferguson Observatory\, 2605 Adobe Canyon Rd\, Kenwood\, CA 95452\, USA
DESCRIPTION:Purchase tickets at <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://rfo.simpletix.com&sa=D&source=calendar&ust=1757458869109324&usg=AOvVaw2iTPgyLdxjSj72OlOZaJf1" target="_blank">rfo.simpletix.com</a>.<br>Presentations on astronomical topics are given in the classroom throughout the course of the evening. Starting at dusk\, the Observatory’s three main telescopes are open for your viewing. Docents set up additional telescopes in front of the building. Friendly and knowledgeable docents are available to answer your questions. $15.00 per adult\; $10.00 for seniors 62+ and students\; $5 youth 6 to 12\; 5 and under FREE. (Plus State Park Parking Fee $10.00 per vehicle.) <br><u></u><u></u>
END:VEVENT
